sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Prime as Prime<br/>(Code Factory)
    participant LLM as LLM API
    participant Supervisor as Supervisor<br/>(Host)
    participant Lab as Lab Container<br/>(Test Rig)

    rect rgb(234, 242, 248)
        Note over User,Lab: Phase 1 — Read Spec
        Note right of Prime: Load CAMBRIAN-SPEC-002.md<br/>from local filesystem.<br/>Load generation history<br/>and fitness log.
    end

    rect rgb(244, 236, 247)
        Note over User,Lab: Phase 2 — Generate
        Prime->>+LLM: Spec + generation history + fitness
        Note right of LLM: Produce complete codebase<br/>from spec. All source files,<br/>build config, tests.
        LLM-->>-Prime: Complete codebase (file set)
        Note right of Prime: Write files to workspace/<br/>Run build step<br/>Create manifest.json<br/>(spec-hash, artifact-hash,<br/>model, token-usage, files)<br/>git commit to gen-N branch
    end

    rect rgb(234, 250, 241)
        Note over User,Lab: Phase 3 — Verify
        Prime->>+Supervisor: POST /spawn {spec-hash, generation, artifact-path}
        Note right of Supervisor: 1. Create Lab container<br/>2. Mount artifact at /workspace<br/>3. Start container
        Supervisor->>Lab: container run lab-gen-N<br/>--volume artifact:/workspace
        activate Lab
        Note right of Lab: Test rig executes:<br/>1. Build — compile/install<br/>2. Unit test — run suite<br/>3. Start — launch Prime,<br/>   wait for port bind (30s)<br/>4. Health — GET /health → 200<br/>   GET /stats → valid JSON
        Note right of Lab: Write viability-report.json<br/>to /workspace/<br/>Exit 0 (viable) or 1 (non-viable)
        deactivate Lab
        Note right of Supervisor: Read /workspace/viability-report.json<br/>Destroy Lab container<br/>Record in generation history
        Supervisor-->>-Prime: Viability report
    end

    alt Viable
        rect rgb(234, 250, 241)
            Note over User,Lab: Phase 4A — Promote
            Prime->>+Supervisor: POST /promote {generation: N}
            Note right of Supervisor: git tag gen-N<br/>Record outcome: promoted<br/>Append fitness log
            Supervisor-->>-Prime: 200 {ok, generation}
        end
    else Non-viable
        rect rgb(253, 237, 236)
            Note over User,Lab: Phase 4B — Rollback
            Prime->>+Supervisor: POST /rollback {generation: N}
            Note right of Supervisor: Discard gen-N branch<br/>Record outcome: failed
            Supervisor-->>-Prime: 200 {ok, generation}
        end
    end

    rect rgb(254, 249, 231)
        Note over User,Lab: Reproductive Test (M1 acceptance)
        Note right of Prime: If promoted generation is Prime:<br/>  Start promoted Prime in new container<br/>  Ask it to generate from the same spec<br/>  Verify THAT offspring is also viable<br/><br/>If offspring can reproduce → M1 complete
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over User,Lab: Bootstrap Path (Stage 0 → Stage 2)
        Note over User,Prime: Stage 0: Human writes bootstrap + test rig + supervisor
        Note over Prime,LLM: Stage 1: Bootstrap reads spec → LLM → first Prime
        Note over Prime,Lab: Stage 2: Prime reads spec → LLM → second Prime
        Note over User,Lab: Accept: Stage 2 output passes same test rig as Stage 1
    end
